    "system": "Renal & GU",
    "topic": "Oxalate stone risk factors",
    "stem": "A 30-year-old man with longstanding Crohn disease and chronic diarrhea presents with recurrent calcium oxalate kidney stones. What best explains his increased stone risk?",
