    "system": "Renal & GU",
    "topic": "PDE5 inhibitor and nitrate contraindication",
    "stem": "A 58-year-old man with erectile dysfunction and stable angina asks about starting sildenafil. He takes isosorbide mononitrate daily. What is the best next step?",
