    "system": "Renal & GU",
    "topic": "Poststreptococcal GN timing",
    "stem": "A 7-year-old boy develops tea-colored urine and periorbital edema 2 weeks after a documented streptococcal pharyngitis. What is the most likely diagnosis?",
