    "system": "Heme/Onc",
    "topic": "DIC diagnosis",
    "stem": "A patient with septic shock develops oozing from IV sites and petechiae. Labs show platelets 40,000/uL, prolonged PT/PTT, fibrinogen 80 mg/dL, elevated D-dimer, and schistocytes on smear. What is the best initial management?",
