    "system": "Dermatology",
    "topic": "Dermatomyositis workup",
    "stem": "A 55-year-old woman has a violaceous rash on her upper eyelids, a rash over her shoulders and upper back, and scaly papules over her knuckles, along with proximal muscle weakness. Which test is most useful to confirm the diagnosis?",
