    "system": "Dermatology",
    "topic": "Erythrasma",
    "stem": "A 52-year-old obese man with diabetes has a well-demarcated reddish-brown patch with fine scale in the groin folds bilaterally, mildly pruritic. Wood's lamp exam shows coral-red fluorescence. What is the most likely diagnosis?",
