    "system": "Health Maintenance & Prevention",
    "topic": "Chlamydia retest timing",
    "stem": "A 26-year-old man is treated for chlamydia urethritis with appropriate antibiotics and reports resolution of symptoms. When should he be retested for chlamydia?",
